The UI is too cluttered and seems to follow differing principles for Backup and for Restore.

We will need a distinct upload for space and global backups. When currently restoring a backup you will have to check twice whether you restore only a space or a global backup which will overwrite the content in the whole instance. 

On a space level it is unclear that the XML export will allow for a proper restore via the administration section. A simple backup button should be added in addition to the existing XML export.

